      "title": "OpenAI 论文：GPT-5.6 Sol Ultra 证明图论\"循环双覆盖猜想\"",
      "title_en": "GPT-5.6 Sol Ultra 给出了\"循环双覆盖猜想\"的证明 【pdf】",
      "url": "https://cdn.openai.com/pdf/04d1d1e4-bc75-476a-97cf-49055cd98d31/cdc_proof.pdf",
