      "title": "Google 推出 LiteRT.js：高性能 Web AI 推理运行时",
      "title_en": "LiteRT.js， Google's high performance Web AI Inference",
      "url": "https://developers.googleblog.com/litertjs-googles-high-performance-web-ai-inference",
      "permalink": "https://aihot.virxact.com/items/cmre0j0vj002sihwk71qvktk7",
      "source": "Google Developers Blog（RSS）",
      "publishedAt": "2026-07-09T21:21:08.292Z",
      "summary": "Google 发布 LiteRT.js，这是 LiteRT 跨平台边缘 AI 运行时的最新成员，专为 JavaScript 开发者设计，可直接在浏览器中运行机器学习模型。LiteRT.js 基于 WebGPU 和即将推出的 WebNN 实现 SOTA 推理性能，同时支持回退到 WebAssembly CPU 方案。",
      "category": "c6",
      "score": 62,
      "selected": true,
      "attribution": {
        "source": "AI HOT",
