      "title": "智能免费，然后呢？--Data Systems for， of， and by Agents",
      "title_en": "Intelligence is Free， Now What？ <br> Data Systems for， of， and by Agents",
      "url": "http://bair.berkeley.edu/blog/2026/07/07/intelligence-is-free-now-what",
