      "fullContent": "Elon Musk on X: \"Grok Imagine update\" / X\nPost\nLog in Sign up\nPost\nElon Musk\n@elonmusk\nGrok Imagine update\ntetsuo\n@tetsuoai\n7月7日\nUpdate your Grok app! 15 Second Imagine videos now available and the quality is incredible.\n00:00\n6:23 · 2026年7月7日 260万 Views\n1 . 7 K 1.7K\n2 . 2 K 2.2K\n7 . 8 K 7.8K\n3 5 3 353\nRead 1689 replies\nSign up with Google Sign up with Apple Create account\nBy signing up, you agree to the Terms of Service and Privacy Policy , including Cookie Use.\nRelevant people\nElon Musk @ elonmusk Follow\nTrending now\nDon't miss what's happening\nPeople on X are the first to know.\nLog in Sign up"
